1
00:00:18,559 --> 00:00:20,000
All three arrows hit the target.

2
00:00:20,199 --> 00:00:21,920
So impressive.

3
00:00:21,920 --> 00:00:23,320
You're good at everything.

4
00:00:24,440 --> 00:00:25,359
Wanna try?

5
00:00:26,440 --> 00:00:27,600
You used to say

6
00:00:28,120 --> 00:00:29,120
that women can do

7
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:31,000
everything men can do.

8
00:00:32,320 --> 00:00:33,759
Let's see if you still

9
00:00:34,359 --> 00:00:35,679
have that spirit.

10
00:00:42,359 --> 00:00:43,079
Missed.

11
00:00:44,119 --> 00:00:44,920
You're still better.

12
00:00:46,600 --> 00:00:48,159
It must be because the mouth of the pot is too small.

13
00:00:48,479 --> 00:00:49,719
I can't throw it in.

14
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:51,840
You can't blame the pot for missing.

15
00:00:58,600 --> 00:00:58,880
Take it.

16
00:01:03,240 --> 00:01:03,960
Be serious.

17
00:01:07,959 --> 00:01:08,959
Keep your back straight.

18
00:01:10,079 --> 00:01:11,120
Hold it steady.

19
00:01:12,719 --> 00:01:13,840
Breathe evenly.

20
00:01:14,959 --> 00:01:15,920
Before throwing,

21
00:01:18,359 --> 00:01:19,519
take a deep breath.

22
00:01:22,719 --> 00:01:23,239
Three,

23
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:24,799
two,

24
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:25,760
one!

25
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,719
You hit the target!

26
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:33,799
Congratulations!

27
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,000
Congratulations!

28
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:39,000
[That arrow hit the target,]

29
00:01:41,560 --> 00:01:43,920
[but it was just a ruse to lure him closer.]

30
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:48,359
[I really underestimated this girl.]

31
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:07,840
My Lady,

32
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:11,159
Lady Liu wants to seize the Xiao Family's wealth.

33
00:02:11,479 --> 00:02:12,400
[We're close,]

34
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,120
[she'll definitely take action.]

35
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,759
Since you came here,

36
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:20,719
we haven't had a proper chat.

37
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,280
You've got good taste.

38
00:02:24,919 --> 00:02:25,719
This girl

39
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,560
looks so lively.

40
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:28,719
Yeah.

41
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,680
Thank you, Madam.

42
00:02:31,919 --> 00:02:32,800
I'm too flattered.

43
00:02:33,919 --> 00:02:34,400
I only wish

44
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,560
to serve the Xiao Family with all my heart.

45
00:02:39,080 --> 00:02:40,840
You're a sensible and well-mannered girl.

46
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:42,960
Don't blame Xiao.

47
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:45,879
Both families are in mourning now.

48
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,520
The marriage should not be rushed.

49
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:51,280
We'll discuss it further after this.

50
00:02:53,599 --> 00:02:55,039
It's entirely up to you, my lady.

51
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,280
My lady.

52
00:03:02,879 --> 00:03:03,719
My lady.

53
00:03:04,039 --> 00:03:04,719
It's nothing.

54
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:06,000
It's just an old ailment.

55
00:03:06,439 --> 00:03:07,479
Word has spread throughout the city

56
00:03:07,759 --> 00:03:09,280
that you are skilled in medicine.

57
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:11,280
Could you take a look at her?

58
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:19,919
My lady,

59
00:03:20,759 --> 00:03:21,599
do you experience

60
00:03:22,080 --> 00:03:23,199
back pain, weakness,

61
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,719
sharp abdominal pain,

62
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,080
and loss of appetite?

63
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,759
I've taken some medicine before,

64
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:30,879
but...

65
00:03:31,759 --> 00:03:33,159
Does Madam Yin have a solution?

66
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,039
My lady,

67
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:39,840
I will do my best to try.

68
00:03:41,199 --> 00:03:42,080
However, fibroids

69
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:43,960
are a particularly difficult condition

70
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,360
to treat in leukorrhea.

71
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,360
It's not something that can be cured overnight.

72
00:03:47,680 --> 00:03:48,199
My lady,

73
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,560
you must be prepared

74
00:03:49,719 --> 00:03:50,479
for a long-term commitment.

75
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:53,159
Then I'll be counting on you, Madam Yin.

76
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,319
Are you alright?

77
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,439
What are you thinking about?

78
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,199
How's the investigation

79
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,399
with the guild?

80
00:04:52,879 --> 00:04:54,160
There was indeed a new deposit.

81
00:04:56,639 --> 00:04:57,639
That means

82
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,000
they are

83
00:04:59,519 --> 00:05:00,639
suspected of

84
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:01,879
both the medicine and the pill.

85
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,160
Or,

86
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:06,360
Ms Liu colluded with the guild

87
00:05:06,959 --> 00:05:08,680
and acted under the name of Xiao Family.

88
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,439
You can leave such chores

89
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:20,120
to the servants.

90
00:05:21,439 --> 00:05:22,480
When did you

91
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,120
start to care about me?

92
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,120
I mean,

93
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,560
if I don't do such chores,

94
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:36,000
how can she

95
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,360
set me up

96
00:05:36,360 --> 00:05:37,240
in this way?

97
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:48,040
My lady,

98
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,360
what's wrong with you?

99
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:51,040
Madam Yin,

100
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,240
after the matriarch took your medicine,

101
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,920
she's been in severe pain,

102
00:05:55,439 --> 00:05:56,399
sweating cold sweats.

103
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:57,959
How could this be?

104
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:58,600
Xinyue,

105
00:05:59,399 --> 00:05:59,879
tell me,

106
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,480
what's really going on?

107
00:06:01,839 --> 00:06:02,800
Yunzhou,

108
00:06:03,199 --> 00:06:04,279
calm down.

109
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:06,199
I believe

110
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:07,199
Madam Yin

111
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,839
didn't mean to do it.

112
00:06:10,639 --> 00:06:11,240
Yunzhou,

113
00:06:11,519 --> 00:06:12,160
trust me.

114
00:06:12,879 --> 00:06:13,560
My lady,

115
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,439
may I take a closer look?

116
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,160
Madam Yin,

117
00:06:25,399 --> 00:06:26,800
you're so cruel.

118
00:06:27,199 --> 00:06:27,920
The Matriarch trusted you,

119
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,600
yet you poisoned her!

120
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,519
I...

121
00:06:30,959 --> 00:06:32,000
Tell me,

122
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:34,439
what poison did you administer?

123
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:35,639
I...

124
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:37,519
Auntie,

125
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,040
how can you be so certain

126
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,279
that I poisoned her?

127
00:06:40,639 --> 00:06:41,519
You prescribed the medicine,

128
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,439
and you prepared it.

129
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,519
Who else could it be?

130
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:46,399
Yunzhou,

131
00:06:46,399 --> 00:06:47,000
I didn't.

132
00:06:48,759 --> 00:06:49,959
I swear I didn't.

133
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,079
My medicine

134
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,759
was accidentally broken.

135
00:06:53,319 --> 00:06:53,720
It must be...

136
00:06:54,319 --> 00:06:55,439
It must be a mistake by a servant,

137
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,480
or

138
00:06:56,959 --> 00:06:58,279
someone wanted to harm the Matriarch

139
00:06:58,759 --> 00:07:00,839
and tried to frame me.

140
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,279
I swear I didn't!

141
00:07:02,279 --> 00:07:02,839
Yunzhou,

142
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,879
since you've said that,

143
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,399
I'll give you another chance.

144
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:09,439
If you can't cure her,

145
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,360
your days in the Xiao Mansion

146
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,439
will be tough.

147
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,839
It must be a servant's mistake.

148
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,279
I trust you.

149
00:07:19,040 --> 00:07:19,959
Let's just

150
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:22,240
leave it at that.

151
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,240
You're so kind

152
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:27,800
not to hold a grudge.

153
00:07:28,839 --> 00:07:29,800
Thank you.

154
00:07:30,879 --> 00:07:31,279
But

155
00:07:33,240 --> 00:07:34,319
plotting against you

156
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:35,480
and framing someone else,

157
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,279
such treachery

158
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,639
can't just be swept under the rug.

159
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,720
He's right.

160
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:42,759
This matter

161
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,639
concerns Lady's safety,

162
00:07:44,879 --> 00:07:46,240
my reputation and life.

163
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,120
If it can't be resolved,

164
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:49,360
today,

165
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,199
he could harm Lady,

166
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,160
tomorrow,

167
00:07:52,439 --> 00:07:53,480
who knows if he won't harm you,

168
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,079
or others in the household?

169
00:07:56,959 --> 00:07:57,519
Xinyue,

170
00:07:57,600 --> 00:07:59,279
I urge you to investigate this thoroughly.

171
00:07:59,399 --> 00:07:59,800
A'Nong,

172
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,439
investigate everyone who has come into contact

173
00:08:01,439 --> 00:08:03,079
with her food and medicine today.

174
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:04,959
I'd like to see

175
00:08:05,639 --> 00:08:07,639
who has the audacity

176
00:08:08,160 --> 00:08:10,040
to stir up trouble in my residence.

177
00:08:10,720 --> 00:08:11,160
Yes.

178
00:08:11,759 --> 00:08:12,360
Alright,

179
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:13,639
I'm going to rest.

180
00:08:14,639 --> 00:08:16,920
You should also return to your quarters.

181
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:18,399
Yes, ma'am.

182
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:23,959
Thank you, Madam.

183
00:08:37,919 --> 00:08:39,080
We still have such a tacit understanding

184
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:40,879
after so many years.

185
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,679
So cold.

186
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:59,000
Give me back my handkerchief.

187
00:09:03,960 --> 00:09:05,519
How about finding a chance

188
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,279
to ask her out alone?

189
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,240
In the deserted garden behind the mountain.

190
00:09:10,159 --> 00:09:11,279
No one will know.

191
00:09:11,639 --> 00:09:12,399
No one will know.

192
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,720
Do you think Xiao Jingyi is a fool?

193
00:09:15,480 --> 00:09:16,440
After this,

194
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:19,639
I'm afraid they've already suspected me.

195
00:09:26,559 --> 00:09:28,080
Have you checked all the herbs?

196
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:29,799
Are there any discrepancies

197
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:30,879
in their origins?

198
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,519
We did find a batch

199
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:34,440
of substandard herbs

200
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,879
of unknown origin.

201
00:09:36,039 --> 00:09:37,000
They've been removed and sealed.

202
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,799
You've found a great wife.

203
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:40,279
If it weren't for her reminder,

204
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,320
it could have caused a disaster.

205
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,559
With Madam Yin in charge,

206
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,120
the Xiao Family will surely thrive.

207
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,279
Maybe you're the one who's truly helpful.

208
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:47,559
Nong?

209
00:09:50,759 --> 00:09:51,240
Yin Shifeng?

210
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:52,360
Wasn't he dead?

211
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,000
Stop!

212
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,919
Have you seen a rich merchant pass by?

213
00:10:24,159 --> 00:10:25,240
No.

214
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,159
Let's go.

215
00:10:41,120 --> 00:10:43,559
Are you really lying to me?

216
00:10:58,159 --> 00:10:58,639
I...

217
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:01,200
I made some burn ointment for you.

218
00:11:08,480 --> 00:11:10,519
Did you make it yourself?

219
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,080
Did you make it specially for me?

220
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:21,879
How much have you drunk?

221
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:34,399
Help me apply the medicine.

222
00:11:59,159 --> 00:12:00,039
If your father...

223
00:12:01,519 --> 00:12:02,960
If your father were alive...

224
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:04,679
My father didn't die.

225
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,360
But my father died.

226
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,399
He died in front of me.

227
00:12:22,759 --> 00:12:23,399
Do you know

228
00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:28,279
Yin Shifeng has secretly met a foreign merchant many times?

229
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:28,759
I know.

230
00:12:33,759 --> 00:12:34,559
You know?

231
00:12:36,639 --> 00:12:37,320
What else do you know?

232
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,440
You're drunk.

233
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:08,759
I'm not.

234
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,039
Are you crazy?

235
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:15,480
Yes,

236
00:13:16,919 --> 00:13:17,799
I am.

237
00:13:19,240 --> 00:13:20,120
I thought

238
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,320
your father saved my father,

239
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:25,399
so he asked me to marry you.

240
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,759
I thought I misunderstood the Yin Family.

241
00:13:29,639 --> 00:13:31,919
I kept making excuses for you.

242
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:43,519
But it turns out you knew

243
00:13:43,519 --> 00:13:45,440
Yin Shifeng colluded with foreign merchants.

244
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,600
His fake death

245
00:13:49,759 --> 00:13:52,000
was just to gain my sympathy for you.

246
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:54,559
You

247
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:59,720
are nothing but a bunch of liars.

248
00:13:59,759 --> 00:14:01,000
That's just what you think.

249
00:14:09,519 --> 00:14:09,960
Nong.

250
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:15,480
Take Madam Yin away

251
00:14:16,919 --> 00:14:19,080
until she tells the truth.

252
00:14:28,559 --> 00:14:29,639
Take good care of her.

253
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:32,879
I heard that Mr. Xiao

254
00:14:32,919 --> 00:14:33,919
locked up Madam Yin

255
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:37,039
after seeing his old friend.

256
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,360
Instead of taking action,

257
00:14:39,600 --> 00:14:41,399
we should break them

258
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:44,080
from within.

259
00:14:44,919 --> 00:14:46,879
Xiao Jingyi's hatred

260
00:14:47,360 --> 00:14:49,159
will eventually turn into a blade.

261
00:14:50,559 --> 00:14:52,159
But it seems that he

262
00:14:52,639 --> 00:14:53,919
has no intention of harming her.

263
00:14:54,399 --> 00:14:55,519
She's just under house arrest.

264
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:59,240
Why not add fuel to the fire?

265
00:14:59,679 --> 00:15:02,279
I won't let her stir up trouble.

266
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:05,120
Send a letter to the guild for me.

267
00:15:05,879 --> 00:15:06,879
To get rid of weeds,

268
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:09,000
you must dig up the roots.
